replies.body:
I was waiting for someone to point these out. Gold Star! Gragas's book is an {{item:1052}} and Ryze has one more but it's *sneaky*.

Triple gold star for spotting Netherstride Grimoire. Because these skins were designed as a group of RPG style adventurers I thought it would really support the theme to showcase some magical loot they had found whilst exploring dungeons. And what better magical loot than in-game items?

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
